        "subject": "LU-3892 ofd: grab attributes while the object is locked",
        "message": "LU-3892 ofd: grab attributes while the object is locked\n\nsetattr and destroy can race on OST side, so it's possible\nfor ofd_setattr() to apply the attributes and find the\nobject destroyed by getattr time. to work this race around\nwe can refresh attributes with the lock held.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icadee30b22945299d3095d3ca5ead3966b2efb1f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
